githubusercontent.com/arthurio/fastapi-filter/main/docs/swagger-ui.png)\n\nYou can play with examples:\n\n```bash\npip install poetry\npoetry install\npython examples/fastapi_filter_sqlalchemy.py\n```\n\n### Filter\n\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/950449/176737541-0e36b72f-38e2-4368-abfa-8bbc0c82e8ae.mp4\n\n### Order by\n\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/950449/176747056-ea82d6b9-cb3b-43eb-aec7-96ba0bc79e8b.mp4\n\n## Contribution\n\nYou can run tests with `pytest`.\n\n```bash\npip install poetry\npoetry install --extras all\npytest\n```\n\n<img width=\"884\" alt=\"arthur_Arthurs-MacBook-Pro-2___code_fastapi-filter\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/950449/176737623-a77f15d6-4e60-4c06-bdb7-b3d77f346a54.png\">\n"], "modules": [{"name": "fastapi_filter.base", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "fastapi_filter", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "fastapi_filter.FilterDepends", "xref": {"fqname": "fastapi_filter.base.filter.FilterDepends", "project": null}}, {"name": "fastapi_filter.with_prefix", "xref": {"fqname": "fastapi_filter.base.filter.with_prefix", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "fastapi_filter.contrib.mongoengine.filter", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "fastapi_filter.contrib.mongoengine.filter.Filter", "bases": ["BaseFilterModel"], "methods": [{"name": "fastapi_filter.contrib.mongoengine.filter.Filter.sort", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "query", "type": {"name": "QuerySet", "xref": {"fqname": "mongoengine.QuerySet", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "QuerySet", "xref": {"fqname": "mongoengine.QuerySet", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fastapi_filter.contrib.mongoengine.filter.Filter.split_str", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"n